text: Yongning Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Naxi District, Luzhou, Sichuan, China. , it has 7 residential communities and 3 villages under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Sichuan == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Sichuan Category:Luzhou
